Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}經線是流逝的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}四季輪換 染上天藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}緯線是人們的生業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}履地前行 震撼心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫的人民 不斷編織著歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}{\blur3}YOLF (You Only Live Forever) 永恆一族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此度過數百年遙遠悠長的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你再玩的話就做不完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跳下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不需要理那個野丫頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遠離塵世 以織布為生的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被人們稱為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「離別的一族」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 拉欣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞下次一定要跳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對待織物不能那麼粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都濕成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸 採到好花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 看來可以織出鮮艷的色彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紗線…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你為什麼在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我是孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算有我在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是愛哭鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道我們為什麼被叫做「離別的一族」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外表幾乎不會變化 並擁有漫長壽命的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對於普通人來說就像是童話中的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可就在數百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像這樣的存在是隨處可見的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像鳥一樣擁有翅膀的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黎明前歌唱的花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}載著水路移動的巨型魚類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些種族全部與這個世界「離別」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們不斷編織著名為「歲月錦」的織物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要在這裡 你就不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在歲月的流逝中 漸漸模糊的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歲月錦會幫我們記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些不得不道別的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也會在歲月錦裡陪你一起哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會陪我一起…哭泣?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 如果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你離開了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}與外面世界的人相遇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}決不能愛上別人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果愛上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就真的變成孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算相遇了 也會變成孤單一人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離別的一族所背負的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安 瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要忘了今天的紡織
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}花開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是雷納特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是梅薩蒂王國派來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快去通知長老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷納特都穿著鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快保護好歲月錦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和傳聞一樣 真的都是些小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是喜歡這種吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}退下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊索爾師長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個村的村長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這還是頭一次有幸見到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然外表看起來是少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而實際上卻是年齡400歲以上的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們以織布為業 以歲月為梭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是日復一日地重複這樣的生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不應該與你們有這樣的交集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這並不是由你來決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是國王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請跟我們一同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前往梅薩蒂的宮邸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離拉欣大人遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女人 把女人抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敢反抗的 直接殺了也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這隻也得了紅眼病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要管它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在重要的是伊歐夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放我出去 放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跳下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬰兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}淚酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是得有鹽才夠味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是長老那裡的瑪琪亞嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本來是來採購歲月錦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒想到卻被困在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡本是流浪者的聚集地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是被山賊襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 這傢伙還熱乎著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親這種生物還真是偉大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算死了 還是想保護自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放著不管的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快就會在天上團聚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙的歲月錦就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過是個渺小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連布都還算不上的殘片罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 總比他一個人孤零零地活著要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是孤單一人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抓得好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了吧 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算帶他走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我的歲月錦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個孤兒遇到另一個孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太陽公公的味道
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}於離別之晨束起約定之花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs63}別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格 德雷爾 別給我偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過來抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs63}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 一群小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 奧諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乳房…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乳房…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找不到乳房
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個小孩想要撫養孩子明擺著是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是 你的孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫光看外表也不知道年齡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格 德雷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 我是15歲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這孩子的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的女人 奇怪的嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可是女孩的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙是男孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那… 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉 艾瑞  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是親戚的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她會織布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}店裡面有台沒人用的織布機 你就用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是伊歐夫人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然還是瞞不過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還請…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫人的布可以賣個好價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼難得的搖錢樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算求我也不會告訴別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 你明明已經很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還要再去照顧一個伊歐夫的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許吧 不過以後會發生什麼誰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管那孩子在不在都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給 這個星期的份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直以來都受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們家的起司味道就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您客氣了 下星期也請多多關照…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然就是不一樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下下星期也請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個女人要撫養孩子可是很不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的丈夫 被得了紅眼病的雷納特殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親到底是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我… 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真棒 艾瑞爾真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已經是個像樣的媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有這麼靠不住的老媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們幾個 羊圈打掃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了 是老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走 德雷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老媽 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點 屁股伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 叫媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開玩笑的 當我沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾 你剛剛說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再叫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又有一隻雷納特的紅眼病發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們會馬上將它處死 遺骸隔離後焚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深埋到地下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.35,0:23:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在活著的個體還有五隻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迄今為止 梅薩蒂之所以能夠凌駕於鄰國之上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為我們擁有遠古的飛行獸雷納特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果雷納特絕種的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個平衡很快就會被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了保持梅薩蒂的統治力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還需要其它超越常理的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們已經將天選之血弄到手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊索爾 那個小姑娘怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個要成為海澤爾王子妃子的伊歐夫小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們明明長著翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不從這裡飛走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.49,0:24:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.96,0:24:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們會漸漸死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.85,0:24:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被壓抑的感情會灼燒你們的心窩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使你們飽受痛苦 慢慢死去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.21,0:24:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}國王要召見您
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.74,0:24:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.57,0:24:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃 為什麼總是來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡和歲月錦的塔很像
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.88,0:24:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.39,0:25:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}織好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.42,0:25:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有好好寫上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.71,0:25:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.47,0:25:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「奧諾拉 早日康復」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.81,0:25:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.34,0:25:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會用織布代替文字來傳達心意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽出生的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.00,0:25:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我出生的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.83,0:25:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔的媽媽說了 媽媽和其他人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.21,0:25:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在艾瑞爾出生的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.83,0:25:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是用肚子來說話的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.17,0:25:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}癢癢蟲要來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.74,0:25:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咯嘰咯嘰咯嘰咯嘰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.66,0:25:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用肚子說話是放屁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.17,0:25:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs63}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奧諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.19,0:25:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要輕輕地給它蓋上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.67,0:25:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了呢 奧諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.37,0:26:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在爸爸和媽媽結婚的時候奧諾拉就在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.48,0:26:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是人類的話已經有90歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.89,0:26:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的母親真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.72,0:26:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老是鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.12,0:26:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不奇怪 媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親對偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.63,0:26:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈哈 他在說「偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.52,0:26:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像嬰兒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.71,0:26:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的是艾瑞爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.47,0:26:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡母親的男孩是很奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.28,0:26:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不奇怪 偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.55,0:26:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不喜歡媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.94,0:26:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我喜歡媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.51,0:26:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你給我安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.77,0:26:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我討厭蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.58,0:26:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事吧 蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.75,0:27:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相當不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.41,0:27:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 這個月的工資
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.32,0:27:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.04,0:27:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 可以幫我看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.35,0:27:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有個客人拿來了歲月錦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.99,0:27:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.65,0:27:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「梅薩帝的城堡 與王子成婚」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.91,0:27:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「美麗的」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.46,0:27:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「蕾莉雅」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.06,0:27:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.76,0:27:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會和達雷爾說好的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.63,0:27:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓你也一起乘上貨船
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看 是那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.29,0:27:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這或許也是個好機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.95,0:28:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 艾瑞爾要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.97,0:28:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶著孩子長途旅行遠比你想像的還要辛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.71,0:28:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更別說你的情況複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.36,0:28:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾可以放在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.61,0:28:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.58,0:28:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.84,0:28:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 不要挖的太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.60,0:28:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是… 要是奧諾拉活過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.18,0:28:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.77,0:28:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是太淺了會被野狗挖出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.00,0:28:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.75,0:28:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把土蓋上就見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.09,0:29:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要來這裡就能見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.12,0:29:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把土蓋上就不能一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.81,0:29:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要好好誇誇它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.78,0:29:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能夠沒有痛苦 這麼安詳地離開
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.46,0:29:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們都會有這麼一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.40,0:29:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奧諾拉只是生來就要比我們更早迎來這一天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.07,0:29:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.35,0:29:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.48,0:29:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.46,0:29:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.72,0:29:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.30,0:29:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.43,0:29:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.48,0:29:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.88,0:29:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家會比我…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.61,0:30:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會比我… 更早迎來這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.00,0:30:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.78,0:30:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.51,0:30:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我早就知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.62,0:30:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.55,0:30:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰先誰後根本不重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.70,0:30:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.22,0:30:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就連蘭格也是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.12,0:30:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是艾瑞爾的媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.41,0:30:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽是不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.85,0:30:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的媽媽就是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.75,0:30:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想媽媽一定是不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.08,0:30:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.18,0:30:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.34,0:30:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.34,0:30:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.13,0:30:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.59,0:31:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.27,0:31:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在等我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.53,0:31:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好去床上睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.18,0:31:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你變重了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.15,0:31:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.28,0:31:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然有太陽的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.06,0:31:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.26,0:31:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我是艾瑞爾的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.61,0:31:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從今以後我們也一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.10,0:31:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.04,0:31:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.39,0:31:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾已經走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.36,0:32:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的不去送他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.00,0:32:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.28,0:32:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 不是說了不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.40,0:32:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.00,0:32:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 你不是答應過我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.40,0:32:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要好好聽話的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.81,0:32:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.50,0:32:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.14,0:32:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還活著啊 瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.51,0:32:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也還…活著 克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.33,0:32:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂覬覦著伊歐夫人的長生之血
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.80,0:33:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才會襲擊村落
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.22,0:33:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅的事也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.09,0:33:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽 蕾莉雅是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.15,0:33:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他叫你媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.37,0:33:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 並不是我要他這麼叫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.27,0:33:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我並沒有生氣 也沒有要責備你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是想到長老常說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.24,0:33:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我沒忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.52,0:33:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.21,0:34:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天早上會舉辦慶祝王子成婚的盛裝遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.16,0:34:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}王子的列隊會從王宮出發
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.70,0:34:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了和從行宮過來的蕾莉雅會合
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.83,0:34:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會經過這座橋
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞄準這個時機
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.30,0:34:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}襲擊王子乘坐的雷納特製造混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.65,0:34:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁著行宮這邊的戒備鬆散的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.00,0:34:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奪回蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.78,0:34:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶也要看遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.53,0:34:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 下次再看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.92,0:34:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.62,0:34:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.52,0:34:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.17,0:34:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}待在這裡 媽媽就變得不像媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.37,0:34:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.93,0:34:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}癢癢蟲要來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.14,0:34:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咯嘰咯嘰咯嘰咯嘰
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.94,0:35:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們已經將伊歐夫的血統納入了皇室血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.65,0:35:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷納特和伊歐夫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.20,0:35:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}存於現世的遠古傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.44,0:35:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們全都得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如今被神選中的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.28,0:35:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經可以說沒有敵手了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.84,0:35:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}與此同時 海澤爾王子與蕾莉雅妃的結合
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.84,0:36:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也將為梅薩蒂寫下新的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.60,0:37:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.82,0:37:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暗殺者？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.06,0:37:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發生了什麼事!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.04,0:37:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.13,0:37:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.61,0:38:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.44,0:38:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.11,0:38:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.28,0:38:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.13,0:38:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.24,0:38:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 走吧 大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.24,0:38:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.47,0:38:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經走不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.48,0:38:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.84,0:38:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.88,0:38:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 蕾莉雅你身手敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.05,0:38:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 就算是城堡的高牆也可以飛過去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.52,0:38:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經不能見克里姆了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.97,0:38:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.66,0:38:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.72,0:38:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.92,0:38:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走 瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.08,0:38:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 蕾莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.46,0:39:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.49,0:39:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 我不是還能飛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.82,0:39:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別讓她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.54,0:39:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.06,0:39:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}追！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.41,0:39:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.74,0:39:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們要是敢對她出手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.72,0:39:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.08,0:39:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定可以飛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.86,0:39:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個嬰兒長大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.04,0:39:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果還活著應該有6歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.71,0:40:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣 外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.73,0:40:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是 伊歐夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.14,0:40:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然只有一半啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.42,0:40:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉欣她
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.80,0:40:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老之所以把伊歐夫人離開村子作為禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.92,0:40:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為她知道伊歐夫人離開村子後的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.30,0:40:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管本人是否願意
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.97,0:40:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和其他人不一樣就會被另眼相待 被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.47,0:40:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後就會被討厭 排擠
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.33,0:40:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 離別的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.59,0:40:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是始終與離別相伴的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.29,0:40:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}願你有個不太糟的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.55,0:41:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆 你的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.58,0:41:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少把外套脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.61,0:41:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬰兒… 是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.94,0:41:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成為母親 又是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.76,0:41:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我到底算不算母親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.21,0:41:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.78,0:41:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是米多教會我的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.60,0:41:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子會幫我忙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.49,0:41:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺就像是弟弟一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.44,0:41:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 又有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.48,0:41:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾要是笑的話 我也會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.09,0:41:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.48,0:41:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我陪在艾瑞爾身邊就能讓他笑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.57,0:41:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和他一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.54,0:42:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這話真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.19,0:42:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明他會比你先死
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.42,0:42:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明他會丟下你一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.44,0:42:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別弄哭她！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.27,0:42:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs63}不許弄哭媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.59,0:42:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.98,0:42:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.04,0:42:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.65,0:42:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能保護得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.56,0:42:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.91,0:42:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要留在梅薩蒂 救出蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.45,0:42:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶著孩子的你會拖累我們
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.06,0:43:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.59,0:43:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.39,0:43:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.69,0:43:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.45,0:43:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.67,0:43:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兩個要去新的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.53,0:43:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.05,0:43:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去米多和蘭格哥哥都不在的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.82,0:43:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起哦 可能再也見不到他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.65,0:43:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只要有媽媽就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.13,0:43:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽也是 有艾瑞爾在就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.11,0:43:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.81,0:43:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們一定是有什麼隱情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.65,0:43:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}萬一出了什麼問題你們又一下子跑了 我可吃不消
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.20,0:43:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.08,0:43:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.44,0:43:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.46,0:44:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽還要去別的地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.14,0:44:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在這個旅館的房間裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.28,0:44:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.22,0:44:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等著我 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.94,0:44:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.84,0:44:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們店主要是做酒吧的 所以會工作到深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.31,0:44:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.27,0:44:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深夜嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.33,0:44:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.04,0:44:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.29,0:44:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還很小…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.03,0:44:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前辭職的女孩也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.95,0:44:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年輕人做事真的是不思前想後
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.75,0:44:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.37,0:44:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.67,0:44:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有作為母親的自覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.05,0:44:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.64,0:44:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡沒有能交給你這種人做的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.31,0:45:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.55,0:45:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.33,0:45:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.95,0:45:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你說 歲月錦…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.40,0:45:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要再給我找事了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.77,0:45:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼擅自拿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.60,0:45:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看一下嘛 媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.43,0:45:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.05,0:45:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 剛才也給我添亂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.02,0:45:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我找不到工作的話 連飯都沒得吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.71,0:45:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.91,0:45:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要讓我頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.94,0:45:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.01,0:45:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}癢癢蟲要來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.56,0:45:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咯嘰咯嘰咯嘰咯嘰
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.02,0:45:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我買了晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.24,0:46:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.73,0:46:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.31,0:46:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我根本沒有作為母親的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.37,0:46:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是在模仿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.98,0:46:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是米多在幫我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.65,0:46:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}決不能愛上別人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.04,0:46:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果愛上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.56,0:46:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就真的變成孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.14,0:46:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.84,0:46:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孤單一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.40,0:46:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽… 媽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.71,0:46:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.64,0:47:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.92,0:47:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.15,0:47:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.09,0:47:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.38,0:47:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.22,0:47:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.24,0:47:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.44,0:47:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.92,0:47:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你上當啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.33,0:47:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一定以為是我脫的殼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.62,0:47:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脫殼算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.98,0:47:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs63}你笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.07,0:47:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.59,0:47:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.23,0:47:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.46,0:48:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是一直這樣不會長大該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.45,0:48:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.71,0:48:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不長大的話就保護不了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.64,0:48:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽你又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.71,0:48:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.53,0:48:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.28,0:48:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.96,0:48:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.85,0:48:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾也是 說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.30,0:48:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.68,0:48:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要保護媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.93,0:49:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.65,0:49:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.50,0:49:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.04,0:49:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.60,0:49:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 上次欠我的要好好還清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.12,0:49:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.08,0:49:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就只會吹噓自己的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.71,0:49:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪有 別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.87,0:49:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個角度要通過經驗去記住
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.93,0:49:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我早說讓你放棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.51,0:49:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還以為會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.28,0:50:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.92,0:50:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞 三個凱爾派
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.23,0:50:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.46,0:50:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.46,0:50:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.84,0:50:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.95,0:50:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小姐姐屁股真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.36,0:50:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.86,0:50:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 你們倆長的並不像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.58,0:50:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你們來這快一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.83,0:50:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前住在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.68,0:50:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.88,0:50:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 有人說你們是謊稱姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.59,0:50:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實是在私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.24,0:50:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.76,0:50:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.19,0:50:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.05,0:50:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又來了一批新的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.44,0:50:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底要派多少人來才放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.54,0:50:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 現在是軍閥的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.20,0:51:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多虧了梅薩蒂拚命地造大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.87,0:51:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們才能吃得上飯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.96,0:51:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過還是有點不尋常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.93,0:51:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是要準備發動戰爭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.44,0:51:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個傻瓜王子有能力指揮軍隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.48,0:51:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.75,0:51:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們一直都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.72,0:51:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 這麼吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.42,0:51:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天就請從這上面選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.19,0:51:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.76,0:51:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.37,0:52:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是瑪琪亞啊 一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.47,0:52:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.99,0:52:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格你變了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.92,0:52:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼能長那麼長
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.41,0:52:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別把我說得像小麥一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.90,0:52:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.89,0:52:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是蘭格啊 蘭格哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.72,0:52:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是艾瑞爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.93,0:52:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然拜訪真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.54,0:52:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事 這麼亂 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.67,0:52:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.22,0:52:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米多和德雷爾都過得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.40,0:52:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.40,0:52:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過景氣的只有像特雷爾這樣的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.94,0:52:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鄉下全都衰落了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.82,0:52:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}德雷爾也離開了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.22,0:52:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.64,0:52:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}德雷爾也在找工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.78,0:52:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不然就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.11,0:52:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.16,0:53:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼 要和女孩子約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.64,0:53:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 要上夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.20,0:53:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上小心 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.49,0:53:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會給你準備簡餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.78,0:53:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他來這之後就開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.00,0:53:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的非常的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.15,0:53:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.84,0:53:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又不能去賣歲月錦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.64,0:53:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 因為我的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.91,0:53:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒辦法一直待在一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.85,0:53:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.67,0:53:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他應該也察覺到你們沒有血緣關係了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.83,0:53:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是在五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.81,0:53:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他提出要分開睡的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.35,0:53:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就不再叫我媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.24,0:53:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是用「喂」「過來一下」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.62,0:54:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老是這麼叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.01,0:54:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正好是這個年紀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.82,0:54:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也曾經有過
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.76,0:54:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格 你知道蕾莉雅怎麼樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.46,0:54:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.81,0:54:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連骨頭也一起燒了 再把灰埋到地底深處
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.18,0:54:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.60,0:54:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 梅德梅爾公主
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.78,0:54:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.03,0:54:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海澤爾王子是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.09,0:54:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.58,0:54:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅爾公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.40,0:54:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.35,0:54:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}據說伊歐夫人頭髮是皎月的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.43,0:54:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞳孔中有金色的輪廓
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.47,0:54:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}體溫也比正常人要低
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.08,0:55:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些特徵在梅德梅爾小姐身上都沒有出現
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.94,0:55:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.09,0:55:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即沒有嫡子 也不能繼承長壽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.80,0:55:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那要那個怪物到底有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.61,0:55:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在生了梅德梅爾小姐之後 就懷不上孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.79,0:55:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海澤爾王子好像也對蕾莉雅妃厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.90,0:55:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊 可憐的海澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.40,0:55:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.79,0:55:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起碼再給他找個新的替代
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.88,0:55:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.66,0:55:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在需要找到伊歐夫人的倖存者作為新的受孕對象
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.32,0:55:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.46,0:55:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.92,0:55:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不戴這些花枝招展的首飾
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.64,0:55:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就連碰都不想碰我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.81,0:55:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就把我趕出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.04,0:55:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃她…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.29,0:55:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.99,0:55:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷納特死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.21,0:55:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.43,0:56:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從生了梅德梅爾之後
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.48,0:56:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就一直被關在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.12,0:56:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就連見她一面都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.53,0:56:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和雷納特一定是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.54,0:56:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是只能在傳說中存在的 虛無飄渺的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.48,0:56:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管是天翔一族 還是在黎明前歌唱的花
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.33,0:56:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這個世界都是無法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.60,0:56:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但起碼還可以掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.11,0:56:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了留下傳說而掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.17,0:56:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.06,0:56:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明就是你 把這個傳說給毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.65,0:57:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請讓我來贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.21,0:57:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.56,0:57:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就讓我見見梅德梅爾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.16,0:57:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不讓我見她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.80,0:57:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是我的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.99,0:57:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經連她的味道都快忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.23,0:57:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連抱著她的時候那柔軟的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.96,0:57:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.82,0:57:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們到底要從我身上奪走多少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.90,0:57:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們就這麼想我孤零零一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.07,0:57:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不能見梅德梅爾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.62,0:57:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就把瑪琪亞帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.25,0:57:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.05,0:57:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把伊歐夫的瑪琪亞帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.62,0:57:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經不想再孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.58,0:58:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你弄的真仔細啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.96,0:58:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為從來沒有客人來過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.28,0:58:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直都是我們兩個在住
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.02,0:58:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過來幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.10,0:58:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你又長高了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.21,0:58:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.61,0:58:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞 我有話和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.03,0:58:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結束之後能抽點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.63,0:58:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是還…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.89,0:58:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會慢慢喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.34,0:58:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞 趕快去點單
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.23,0:58:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.73,0:59:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以為是你的女人才沒有出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.31,0:59:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.96,0:59:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好男人不是有很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.28,0:59:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然被那種傢伙搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.73,0:59:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人不是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.12,0:59:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.62,0:59:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺好沉悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.69,0:59:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.76,0:59:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.75,0:59:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已經不是孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.00,0:59:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.28,0:59:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那這個應該也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.80,0:59:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 這是加入大人行列的機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.36,0:59:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.31,0:59:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起氣 乾掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.32,0:59:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起氣 乾掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.21,0:59:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.02,0:59:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.33,0:59:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.13,0:59:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成為男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.18,0:59:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在找我？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.17,1:00:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個城市也不能待了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.58,1:00:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要和我一起回農場？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.01,1:00:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.84,1:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.32,1:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羊奶也漲價了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.59,1:00:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也帶艾瑞爾一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.58,1:00:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想給你添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.36,1:00:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.72,1:00:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是把米多和德雷爾也牽連了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.32,1:00:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我就…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.68,1:00:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.78,1:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你能給我添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.96,1:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從小時候開始我就一直想成為你的支柱
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.93,1:00:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你能考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.95,1:00:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以後的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.80,1:00:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.48,1:00:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我之間的事
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.03,1:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得我沒辦法考慮
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.56,1:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我只考慮過艾瑞爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.02,1:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣才能和艾瑞爾一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.22,1:01:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣才能像真正的媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.49,1:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但完全找不到答案
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.92,1:01:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在也還是找不到的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.63,1:01:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我非常笨
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.51,1:01:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以後也想一直考慮艾瑞爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.75,1:01:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.62,1:01:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.28,1:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下去的住處和工作的地方也讓我幫你一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.24,1:01:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要一個人承擔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.50,1:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.15,1:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.97,1:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}酒味好重
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.70,1:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.06,1:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼「我回來了」啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.71,1:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼了 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.92,1:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回家的吻呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.23,1:02:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.47,1:02:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明每次都會親我的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.96,1:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.69,1:02:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.20,1:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別人覺得我們是私奔的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.80,1:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還被新來的男人搶走了女人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.76,1:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.57,1:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快 站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.55,1:03:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要睡的話好好去床上睡
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.28,1:03:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能走嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.74,1:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要踩
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.11,1:03:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是艾瑞爾織給我的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.65,1:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看著就火大
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.31,1:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你為什麼還留著這種東西
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.56,1:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到底還要把我當小孩多久
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.69,1:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永遠都不會變的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.74,1:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.50,1:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.91,1:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.90,1:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們又得搬家了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.34,1:04:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下去你覺得去哪裡好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.46,1:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要和艾瑞爾在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.64,1:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去哪裡都行
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.86,1:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從來沒有把你當成母親
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.78,1:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能幫我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.63,1:05:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我成為城裡的士兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.28,1:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.37,1:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞會傷心的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.92,1:05:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她又不是我的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.03,1:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.21,1:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這句話你對她說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.89,1:05:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.95,1:05:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道瑪琪亞是以怎樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.60,1:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎樣的想法把你撫養長大的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.83,1:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要發嗲了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.49,1:06:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從和你差不多年紀的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.40,1:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞就拚了命地想做好母親
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.22,1:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而你卻…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.12,1:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.29,1:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼那個人會將我看得如此重要
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.68,1:06:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.48,1:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.07,1:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了我拚盡全力
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.47,1:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是覺得這樣的人就叫做母親
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.63,1:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 才叫她媽媽的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.54,1:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想保護她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.06,1:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 現在的我保護不了她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.90,1:06:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不僅如此 還會傷害她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.35,1:06:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我察覺到了這份感情
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.92,1:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}憑我是保護不了她的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.53,1:07:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這麼一哭起來
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.21,1:07:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是和小時候一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.52,1:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.77,1:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了 我自己來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.38,1:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也要出城的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.81,1:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我送你離開之後
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.15,1:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當心點 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.01,1:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一路順風
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.68,1:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.31,1:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.52,1:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.14,1:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們約定好的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.77,1:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾 大騙子
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.89,1:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明說好要保護我的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.44,1:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大騙子
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.87,1:09:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.52,1:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.93,1:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還以為能看到真的雷納特呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.97,1:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.55,1:10:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前明明有很多的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.44,1:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在城裡只有一頭了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.66,1:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用這種紙老虎遊行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.52,1:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼可能鼓舞士氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.59,1:10:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你聽說了嗎 巴耶拉好像把伊歐夫弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.11,1:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巴耶拉？真的假的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.36,1:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}師長大人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.05,1:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要再燒蝨子了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.64,1:11:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好煩
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.03,1:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格師長閣下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.00,1:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是在搜查
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.67,1:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是和蕾莉雅妃年齡相仿的少女
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.28,1:11:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還不一定就是瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.24,1:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.31,1:11:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是個堅強的人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.13,1:11:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是被瑪琪亞聽見了一定會很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.49,1:11:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她一直都在擔心自己是否保護好艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.17,1:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算這樣還是拚盡全力
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.89,1:11:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了讓你認為她是個可靠的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.53,1:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是個小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.73,1:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我或許是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.44,1:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 我也要成為父親
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.45,1:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂王國
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.20,1:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}區區紙老虎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.12,1:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然以遠古之力換取權力
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.06,1:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這般褻瀆 何等愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.52,1:12:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吾國必將傾盡全力來協助您
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.22,1:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.08,1:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.56,1:12:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的頭髮變長了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.82,1:12:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一般伊歐夫只有在生了孩子後
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.46,1:12:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頭髮才可以過腰
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.38,1:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧 瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.92,1:12:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們去接蕾莉雅吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.48,1:13:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要打仗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.75,1:13:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過是一時的痛苦而已
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.43,1:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且你在這幾年
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.31,1:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所受的苦遠比戰爭之苦更甚吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.60,1:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離開伊歐夫的村落
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.16,1:13:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失去了所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.01,1:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個人像死人一般 藏在地窖裡
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.84,1:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.82,1:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這下你總算理解我們的感受了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.14,1:13:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家流離失所
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.10,1:13:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人恐怕也已經不在人世了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.36,1:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們失去了一切 不斷忍受著痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.81,1:13:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而在這期間
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.68,1:13:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有你一直過著幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.28,1:13:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫的人民是要同織一塊布的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.26,1:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 蕾莉雅 以及瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.80,1:13:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三個人的過去必須是一樣的才行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.18,1:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭喜你 瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.40,1:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣 只屬於你的過去就消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.68,1:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們又能共同編織同一個未來了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.12,1:14:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.51,1:14:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回家 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.64,1:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天終於能早點回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.08,1:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 明明現在是關鍵期
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.49,1:14:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還老是讓你等我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.79,1:14:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大夫說還要過些日子才會生呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.11,1:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.99,1:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我還是有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.29,1:14:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我馬上給你準備晚餐
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.17,1:15:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了 別累著 我來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.80,1:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微動一動才好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.77,1:15:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 趕緊坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.61,1:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.97,1:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於快了呢 感覺有點不可思議
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.42,1:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出來找工作 來到梅薩蒂王國
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.04,1:15:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟艾瑞爾再會
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.63,1:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.23,1:15:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 艾瑞爾…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.47,1:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我在一起 真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.02,1:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.46,1:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是巴耶拉王國的船嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.92,1:16:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不只是巴耶拉王國
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.15,1:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有雨果和恩多拉王國
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.64,1:16:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.44,1:16:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你保護好肚子裡的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.90,1:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太慢了 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.35,1:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.31,1:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根據傳來的消息 巴耶拉王國軍已經越過山關了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.08,1:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全員分成兩隊…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.64,1:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是諷刺
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.65,1:17:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂王國
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.94,1:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了炫耀自己的強大 使用了遠古的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.74,1:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而 為了制裁濫用遠古之力的梅薩蒂王國
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.14,1:17:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反而讓鄰國們聯合了起來 導致了這樣的結果
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.51,1:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大臣何在
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.61,1:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說他已經和侍從們一起逃出城外了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.93,1:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道他拋棄了我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.18,1:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.94,1:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經完了 回天乏術了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.99,1:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}陛下 請趕快
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.18,1:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 梅德梅爾公主怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.28,1:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忌諱的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.84,1:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那種東西就扔在這裡陪她母親去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.71,1:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞 快點
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.92,1:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.72,1:19:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.52,1:19:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.03,1:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.48,1:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.95,1:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.46,1:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.09,1:20:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.25,1:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是說 我看到的是…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.40,1:20:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亡靈？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.89,1:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.81,1:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.64,1:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些讓你受苦的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.16,1:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會讓他們嚐到比你更多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.12,1:20:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後一切都將煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.01,1:20:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.29,1:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想見她…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.14,1:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.62,1:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.81,1:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是你本不情願 被迫生下的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.38,1:20:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 那也是我的…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.69,1:20:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要忘掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.44,1:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的歲月錦上並沒有女兒的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.90,1:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.65,1:20:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以為克里姆…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.18,1:21:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.82,1:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以為我失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.99,1:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以一直以來都只去考慮女兒的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.80,1:21:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「想見一見她」
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.98,1:21:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「想抱一抱那孩子」
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.12,1:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}憑著僅有的這些想法
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.78,1:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總算是活了下來
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.92,1:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.81,1:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的…梅德梅爾
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.70,1:21:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.83,1:21:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.86,1:22:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這裡結束吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.94,1:22:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.52,1:22:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能再讓…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.95,1:22:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這群外人…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.11,1:22:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}繼續玷汙我們的…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.88,1:22:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歲月錦了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.48,1:22:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.18,1:22:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.57,1:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.00,1:23:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不論是蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.76,1:23:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.41,1:23:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.98,1:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.66,1:23:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們的時間會前進呢
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.07,1:24:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像那天一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.21,1:24:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.04,1:24:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}師長大人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.89,1:24:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有情報說 在巴耶拉王國的船上
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.56,1:24:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有伊歐夫的少年和少女
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.77,1:24:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你見到她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.13,1:24:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.07,1:24:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你走吧 這裡就交給我們
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.62,1:24:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去保護瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.19,1:24:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要一起戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.56,1:24:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你對梅薩蒂王國這麼忠心耿耿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.25,1:25:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本不是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.51,1:25:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你只是為了逃避瑪琪亞才…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.44,1:25:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.75,1:25:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始確實就像你說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.07,1:25:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是現在 我有了蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.33,1:25:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有了伙伴
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.08,1:25:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有快要出生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.95,1:25:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個梅薩蒂王國
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.48,1:25:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我離開那個人之後
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.05,1:25:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一次得到的容身之處
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.64,1:25:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想要保護它！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.75,1:25:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.30,1:25:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.12,1:25:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去找醫生！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.35,1:25:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.13,1:25:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偏偏在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.38,1:25:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.46,1:26:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是艾瑞爾的…寶寶
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.36,1:26:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開火！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.85,1:26:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開火！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.02,1:26:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.75,1:26:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加油 還差一點
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.68,1:26:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}馬上就能見到小寶寶了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.99,1:27:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這樣 做的很好
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.60,1:27:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔 加把勁
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.72,1:27:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.56,1:27:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.41,1:27:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要怕！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.07,1:27:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.83,1:27:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.63,1:27:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}害怕…好害怕！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.42,1:27:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.15,1:27:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.74,1:27:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.12,1:27:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救孩子！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.79,1:27:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來救你們
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.98,1:27:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會得救的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.82,1:27:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黎明就要來了 進攻！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.83,1:28:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看 是小寶寶哦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.34,1:28:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}馬上就要出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.04,1:28:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔和艾瑞爾 就要成為媽媽和爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.89,1:28:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辛苦了 蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.31,1:28:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.38,1:29:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算帶他走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.92,1:29:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.90,1:29:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.52,1:29:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我的歲月錦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.81,1:29:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.09,1:29:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.27,1:29:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾 差不多該回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.89,1:29:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.80,1:29:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.21,1:29:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你身體都涼透了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.19,1:29:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回家 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.95,1:30:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.46,1:30:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.27,1:30:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是夢？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.08,1:30:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是夢哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.58,1:30:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.56,1:30:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並不是雪哦 是灰
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.90,1:30:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾和蒂塔的寶寶出生了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.37,1:30:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.12,1:30:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係的 她們會等你的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.48,1:30:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她們會好好等你回去的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.89,1:30:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾也是像那樣從母親的腹中誕生的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.64,1:31:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的母親當時緊緊地抱著你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.28,1:31:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手指很用力地緊扣 好不容易才掰開
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.08,1:31:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一根 一根地…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.97,1:31:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.01,1:31:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒能夠成為艾瑞爾的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.36,1:31:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.87,1:31:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你教會了我
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.30,1:31:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溫柔 堅強
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.55,1:31:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.71,1:31:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教會我如何去愛別人
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.97,1:31:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}思考艾瑞爾的事情就像是在思考自己的一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.01,1:31:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在遇到艾瑞爾的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.48,1:32:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得這孩子能陪我一起哭泣
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.42,1:32:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覺得你就是我的歲月錦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.13,1:32:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要和艾瑞爾在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.51,1:32:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就能對各種悲傷和痛苦感到釋懷
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.40,1:32:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我卻…對你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.91,1:32:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾並不是騙子
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.72,1:32:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾遵守了諾言
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.88,1:32:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一直都在保護我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.28,1:32:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算彼此分離 形單影隻
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.92,1:32:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漸漸地迷失了自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.68,1:32:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使如此 只要想起艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.77,1:32:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就能找回自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.80,1:32:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要艾瑞爾願意叫我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.72,1:32:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算不是母親也可以
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.93,1:33:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無論是怎樣的稱呼
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.88,1:33:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那都一定是屬於我的稱呼
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.50,1:33:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把我的人生變得如此完整的 是你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.15,1:33:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.55,1:33:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.26,1:33:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能幫我把艾瑞爾帶回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.27,1:33:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶他回蒂塔和寶寶的身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.47,1:33:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回他自己的家
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.56,1:33:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.93,1:34:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求求你不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.74,1:34:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.18,1:35:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們該下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.14,1:35:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅爾公主
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.59,1:35:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父王他們呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.14,1:35:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.67,1:35:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.40,1:35:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果從這裡下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.08,1:35:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等著我的是和如今截然不同的未來
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.28,1:35:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 即使如此
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.34,1:35:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.80,1:35:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.30,1:35:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.52,1:36:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是 我的母親？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.42,1:36:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是伊歐夫的蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.08,1:36:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放縱不羈 活潑奔放 不讓鬚眉
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.92,1:36:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並且 自由自在
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.36,1:36:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅 快跳
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.69,1:36:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能飛
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.22,1:36:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母后！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.96,1:37:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.28,1:37:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣呀 你也能飛了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.64,1:37:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永別了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.37,1:37:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把我忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.84,1:37:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也會把你忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.97,1:37:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在城中的生活 和這個早晨發生的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.96,1:37:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會出現在我的歲月錦上
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.16,1:37:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母后
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.67,1:37:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在漫長的人生中逐漸遺忘
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.16,1:37:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會永遠忘記這一切
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.08,1:37:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不過是記憶中的些微瑕疵
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.62,1:37:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.86,1:37:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.85,1:37:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母后是個十分美麗的人呢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.95,1:38:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅爾公主
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.17,1:38:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是雷納特
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.01,1:38:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.48,1:38:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不再被需要的雷納特
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.69,1:38:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不再被需要的伊歐夫
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.73,1:38:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古老的生物們終將消逝
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.41,1:38:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼至少最後就讓她們隨心所欲地過吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.42,1:38:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要哭了 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.50,1:38:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.61,1:38:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.95,1:39:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又痛苦又悲傷
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.48,1:39:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是這麼美麗的世界 我怎麼可能忘得了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.94,1:39:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.40,1:39:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回來了？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.43,1:39:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.19,1:39:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我的？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.04,1:39:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.51,1:40:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}軟軟的 有點不敢碰
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.76,1:40:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必須得想個名字了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.28,1:40:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.19,1:40:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.98,1:40:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.80,1:40:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小時候
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.60,1:40:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我居然說你喜歡母親很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.80,1:40:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明一點都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.46,1:40:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為艾瑞爾的母親太過美麗 太過溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.15,1:40:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.06,1:40:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才也為了這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.46,1:40:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.75,1:40:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也愛你 可是我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.99,1:41:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}卻一直嫉妒著艾瑞爾的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.27,1:41:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被母親撫養大的我
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.96,1:41:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛上了你
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.19,1:41:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這孩子一定也會和誰相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.77,1:41:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我們一起撫養他吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.81,1:41:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靠我和蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.51,1:41:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教會他如何去愛別人
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.10,1:41:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離別的一族
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.22,1:41:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見證了無數的離別
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.30,1:41:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見證了無數的變遷
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.43,1:41:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}時間不曾停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.59,1:41:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因如此才能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.05,1:41:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相遇並編織彼此的人生
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.69,1:42:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.65,1:42:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能帶我去你爺爺家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.48,1:42:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.81,1:42:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莉莉
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.57,1:42:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要亂跑 你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.15,1:42:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您是
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.12,1:42:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親3年前去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.34,1:42:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們是一對非常親密的夫妻
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.83,1:42:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂陷落之後
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.91,1:42:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靠著蘭格先生的關係回到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.81,1:42:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然吃了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.76,1:42:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但也算是幸福的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.65,1:42:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.11,1:42:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們經常會提起您的事
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.46,1:42:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每當聊起您的時候的臉上都洋溢著幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.82,1:43:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能趕上真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.39,1:43:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父親已經…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.71,1:43:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.70,1:43:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厲害啊 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.47,1:43:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼長的時間
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.33,1:44:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都努力地活下來了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.57,1:44:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.20,1:44:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會哭的 因為我們約定過
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.61,1:44:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.53,1:44:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.28,1:45:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一路順風 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.40,1:45:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚餐之前記得回來哦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.35,1:45:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.19,1:45:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.17,1:46:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.01,1:46:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.36,1:46:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你聽我說 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.97,1:46:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.78,1:46:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.68,1:46:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你上當了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.91,1:46:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以為是我脫的殼吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.95,1:46:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我出生的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.43,1:46:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}癢癢蟲要來囉
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.63,1:46:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你笑啦…
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.92,1:46:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說媽媽和其他人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.56,1:46:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.53,1:46:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.78,1:46:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.42,1:46:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}待在這裡 媽媽就變得不像媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.13,1:46:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不許弄哭媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.48,1:46:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只要有媽媽就夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.78,1:46:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會保護媽媽的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.03,1:46:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.13,1:46:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.69,1:46:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.33,1:46:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.00,1:46:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了 我自己會做的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.00,1:46:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.84,1:46:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.89,1:46:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.11,1:46:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.91,1:46:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.88,1:46:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.92,1:46:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看著就火大
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.72,1:46:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.30,1:46:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從沒把你當成母親
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.89,1:47:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.66,1:47:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想要保護她
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.67,1:47:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}憑我是保護不了她的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.12,1:47:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼那個人將我看得如此重要
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.24,1:47:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你教會了我
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.37,1:47:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求求你不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.89,1:47:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.75,1:47:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾 對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.63,1:47:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.63,1:47:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.46,1:47:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會再哭了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.33,1:47:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.40,1:47:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.89,1:47:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽 沒能守住約定
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.88,1:47:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.07,1:47:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最喜歡媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.25,1:47:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.14,1:48:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.62,1:48:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.94,1:48:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.19,1:48:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.91,1:48:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要我還活著
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.51,1:48:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的歲月錦就會一直持續下去
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.46,1:48:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不許笑我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.30,1:48:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老要是看到你這張臉也會笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.68,1:48:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然會笑了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.47,1:49:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當你告訴她離別不是只有痛苦的時候一定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.29,1:49:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快上來 出發了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.32,1:49:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了和新的離別相遇
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.88,1:49:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.54,1:49:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能愛上艾瑞爾真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.44,1:49:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛過他 真是太好了
